# Kokoro stress hints — tune for your content

emphasize:
  - not      # contrast word — tested across R4–R5, reliable
  - only     # scope limiter — tested, reliable
  - critical # domain emphasis — add your own content-specific terms

deemphasize: []
# ⚠️ MUST stay empty.
# R4 regression: ~650 (-1) wraps on articles/pronouns/linking verbs
# produced a "timid, reserved" cadence (per listener review).
# Known-unsafe — do NOT re-add:
#   articles: the, a, an
#   pronouns: I, you, it, they, we
#   be-forms: is, are, was, were, be, been
#   filler adverbs: just, really, very, quite
